    "Meanwhile, S is fed into a multi-channel support Algorithm 1 Condition Adversarial Attacks (based on PGD)Require: train samples:T train = {T i } M train i=1, dev samples: D dev = {D i } M dev i=1, perturbation bound:, ascend steps: K, ascend step size: α, learn rate: τ Initialize θ; begin_attack = False; best_ f 1 = 0;for episode i = 1 to M train do S, Q = T i δ 0 = 1 √ N δ U (-,) g 0 = ∇ δ L f θ (X), y if begin_attack then for t = 1 to K do if t = 1 then back up X param data end if X = X + δ t if t!",
